          <p class='first-para'>
            Surely, the problem for farmers is that the structure of the EU predicates against that, because they
            
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_87wh' title='Col. 87WH &mdash; HC Deb 15 October 2003 vol 411 c87WH' name='column_87wh' href='#column_87wh' rel='bookmark'>87WH</a>
